13 June 2022 The Government Communication and Information System in partnership with the National Youth Development Agency will host a Twitter Space Engagement on Youth Entrepreneurship as part of the Youth Month celebrations. The Twitter Space aims to celebrate success stories of young entrepreneurs in an effort to cultivate an entrepreneurial spirit amongst the youth. The session will also empower young people with the right knowledge and resources to enable them to start sustainable businesses and positively contribute towards the growth of the country’s economy. Members of the media are invited to attend the Twitter Space. Details are as follows: Date: Wednesday, 15 June 2022Time: 17h00 – 18h00Platform: Twitter @GCISMediaLink: http://twitter.com/GCISMedia Speakers: Members of the media are requested to confirm their attendance to Ms Vanessa Mokaila on email: Vanessa@gcis.gov.za Enquiries: William Baloyi on 083 390 7147 Issued by the Government Communication and Information System